title: Naufahu Whyte
text:
Naufahu Whyte is a professional <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer who plays as a for the <a href="Sydney%20Roosters">Sydney Roosters</a> in the <a href="National%20Rugby%20League">NRL</a>.
Playing Career.
In round 22 2021, Whyte made his <a href="NRL">NRL</a> debut for the Roosters against the <a href="Brisbane%20Broncos">Brisbane Broncos</a> at <a href="Suncorp%20Stadium">Suncorp Stadium</a> in a 21-20 win. Whyte re-signed with the Roosters until the end of 2024.
